---
// Signals Section (Word Cloud & Magazine Typography)
---

<section id="signals" class="signals">
  <div class="section-layout">
    <div class="section-sidebar">
      <div class="sticky-title fade-in-up">
        <h2 class="section-title">Signals</h2>
        <p>保持敏锐，持续输入</p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="section-content">
      <div class="signals-typography fade-in-up">
        <div class="typography-block" data-tone="signals-mind">
          <h3>On My Mind</h3>
          <p class="insight-text">
            《Vibe Coding 改变的不是效率，而是接口》<br />
            从 prompt 到 directing：AIGC 交互范式的转移。<br />
            当 Agent 具备 Continual Learning 能力时，产品形态会发生什么根本性变化？
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="typography-block mt-lg" data-tone="signals-diet">
          <h3>Information Diet</h3>
          <div class="word-cloud">
            <span class="cloud-item large">Acquired</span>
            <span class="cloud-item medium">Lex Fridman</span>
            <span class="cloud-item small">Stratechery</span>
            <span class="cloud-item large">Andrej Karpathy</span>
            <span class="cloud-item medium">Lenny's Podcast</span>
            <span class="cloud-item small">The Verge</span>
            <span class="cloud-item medium">Not Boring</span>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="typography-block mt-lg" data-tone="signals-stack">
          <h3>Daily Stack</h3>
          <div class="word-cloud tool-cloud">
            <span class="cloud-item">Cursor</span>
            <span class="cloud-item">Arc Browser</span>
            <span class="cloud-item">Figma</span>
            <span class="cloud-item">Linear</span>
            <span class="cloud-item">PyTorch</span>
            <span class="cloud-item">Astro</span>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .signals {
    display: block;
  }

  .section-layout {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    gap: var(--space-md);
  }

  @media (min-width: 1024px) {
    .section-layout {
      grid-template-columns: var(--layout-sidebar-columns);
      gap: var(--space-xl);
    }

    .sticky-title {
      position: sticky;
      top: calc(var(--header-height) + var(--space-xl));
    }
  }

  .section-title {
    margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
    font-size: clamp(2rem, 3vw, 3rem);
    line-height: 1.1;
  }

  /* Typography Style */
  .signals-typography {
    padding-top: var(--space-md);
  }

  .typography-block h3 {
    font-size: 0.85rem;
    font-weight: var(--font-weight-ui);
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 0.05em;
    color: var(--tone-strong, var(--color-text-muted));
    margin-bottom: var(--space-sm);
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--tone-border, var(--color-border));
    padding-bottom: 0.5rem;
    width: max-content;
  }

  .insight-text {
    font-size: clamp(1.1rem, 1.5vw, 1.5rem);
    line-height: 1.6;
    color: color-mix(
      in srgb,
      var(--tone-solid, var(--content-tone-default)) 20%,
      var(--color-text)
    );
    font-weight: var(--font-weight-body);
  }

  /* Word Cloud */
  .word-cloud {
    display: flex;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
    gap: var(--space-sm) var(--space-md);
    align-items: baseline;
  }

  .cloud-item {
    color: var(--tone-strong, var(--color-text));
    transition:
      var(--transition-color-fast),
      transform var(--transition-fast);
    cursor: default;
    display: inline-block;
  }

  .cloud-item:hover {
    color: var(--tone-muted, var(--color-text-muted));
    transform: scale(0.98);
  }

  .cloud-item.large {
    font-size: clamp(2rem, 3vw, 3.5rem);
    font-weight: var(--font-weight-heading);
    letter-spacing: -0.02em;
  }
  .cloud-item.medium {
    font-size: clamp(1.5rem, 2vw, 2.5rem);
    font-weight: var(--font-weight-ui);
  }
  .cloud-item.small {
    font-size: clamp(1rem, 1.2vw, 1.5rem);
    font-weight: var(--font-weight-body);
    color: var(--tone-muted, var(--color-text-muted));
  }

  .tool-cloud .cloud-item {
    font-family: var(--font-mono);
    font-size: clamp(1.2rem, 1.5vw, 2rem);
    font-weight: var(--font-weight-ui);
    text-transform: lowercase;
    opacity: 0.85;
  }
</style>
